### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@thermometerId = thermo-001
@roomId = living-room
@apiKey = change-me

### Get anomalies by thermometer (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/{{thermometerId}}/anomalies
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get anomalies by thermometer (custom pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/{{thermometerId}}/anomalies?page=0&pageSize=10
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get anomalies by thermometer (second page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/{{thermometerId}}/anomalies?page=1&pageSize=5
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get anomalies by room (default pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/rooms/{{roomId}}/anomalies
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get anomalies by room (custom pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/rooms/{{roomId}}/anomalies?page=0&pageSize=10
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get thermometers above anomaly threshold (from specific date)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/thermometers/above-threshold?fromDate=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}

### Get thermometers above anomaly threshold (last 24 hours)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/temperatures/thermometers/above-threshold?fromDate=2025-01-14T00:00:00Z
X-Api-Key: {{apiKey}}
